3. SLUGS Y ESTRUCTURA DE URL (ES/EN)
- ES raíz: /es/
- EN raíz: /en/
- Ejemplos espejo: /es/programas/preescolar/ ↔ /en/programs/preschool/

4. ENLACES INTERNOS PRIORITARIOS
- Home → Programas, Admisiones, Costos, Contacto
- Admisiones → Aplicar, Agendar Visita, FAQ
- Programas → Admisiones, Costos, Contacto
- Blog/Artículos → Programas y Admisiones según contexto
- Eventos → Registro y Contacto

5. SCHEMA MARKUP (JSON-LD)
- Organization / School
- EducationalOrganization (para páginas generales)
- Article (para blog)
- Event (para eventos)
- BreadcrumbList (global)

6. JSON-LD PLANTILLAS (ES)

Organization (global, en Home)
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "EducationalOrganization",
  "name": "Valderrama International School",
  "url": "https://valderramainternationalschool.com/",
  "logo": "https://valderramainternationalschool.com/media/logo.png",
  "address": {
    "@type": "PostalAddress",
    "addressLocality": "Cartagena",
    "addressRegion": "Bolívar",
    "addressCountry": "CO"
  },
  "sameAs": ["https://www.facebook.com/valderramais", "https://www.instagram.com/valderramais"]
}

Article (para un post de blog)
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": "{{post_title}}",
  "image": ["{{featured_image_url}}"],
  "datePublished": "{{post_date}}",
  "author": {"@type": "Person", "name": "{{author_name}}"},
  "publisher": {"@type": "Organization", "name": "Valderrama International School"}
}

Event (para un evento)
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Event",
  "name": "{{event_title}}",
  "startDate": "{{event_start_iso}}",
  "endDate": "{{event_end_iso}}",
  "eventAttendanceMode": "https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode",
  "eventStatus": "https://schema.org/EventScheduled",
  "location": {"@type": "Place", "name": "Valderrama IS", "address": "Cartagena, Colombia"}
}

BreadcrumbList (global)
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Inicio", "item": "https://valderramainternationalschool.com/es/"},
    {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "{{seccion}}", "item": "{{url}}"}
  ]
}

7. MATRIZ SEO (RESUMEN 10 PÁGINAS CLAVE)
- Incluye Title, Description, Slug, H1, Keywords target, Enlaces internos
- Entregable: CSV editable para 33 páginas (adjuntar en planilla)

8. IMÁGENES Y ALT TEXT
- Formato preferido: WebP
- Dimensiones recomendadas: hero 1920×1080, tarjetas 800×600
- Alt text: descriptivo, 7–12 palabras, incluye contexto educativo

9. OPEN GRAPH / TWITTER CARDS
- og:title, og:description, og:image por página
- twitter:card = summary_large_image

10. SITEMAP Y GSC
- Generar sitemap XML (Yoast/RankMath)
- Enviar a Google Search Console (propiedad del dominio)

